{"nodes": [{"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_fase_2a_design", "label": "Fase 2A Design Spec \u2014 Automatic Progression + Workout History", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-02-fase-2a-progresion-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_progressionservice", "label": "ProgressionService (pure backend prescription engine)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-02-fase-2a-progresion-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Progression is computed in the backend (business logic in services) so that in Fase 3 only the history source changes (Mongo); the class is pure with no I/O, making it directly unit-testable."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_double_progression_rpe", "label": "Double Progression Auto-regulated by RPE", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-02-fase-2a-progresion-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Chosen because it is auto-regulated, standard in hypertrophy training, and exploits the RPE the user already logs. Rules: all sets at range top AND avg RPE \u2264 8 \u2192 +weight; any set below range min OR avg RPE \u2265 9.5 \u2192 \u2212weight; otherwise keep weight and target best reps + 1. Increment 5 kg if weight_factor \u2265 1.2 else 2.5 kg; 2.5 kg floor; goal change resets reps to new range minimum."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_history_localstorage", "label": "Workout History in localStorage (fit_poke_history_v1, WorkoutLog[], FIFO cap 100)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-02-fase-2a-progresion-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Stored client-side because there is no auth or DB until Fase 3 and Render has an ephemeral filesystem; workouts with 0 completed sets are not saved; exerciseName is kept so logs survive DB changes."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_history_summary_transport", "label": "ExerciseHistorySummary Compact Transport (last session per exercise, max 30)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-02-fase-2a-progresion-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "A compact summary travels in each /generate and /reroll request: one roundtrip, backend stays stateless, payload is bounded (max 30 entries, 10 sets each)."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_selection_bias_70_30", "label": "70/30 Selection Bias Toward Exercises with History", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-02-fase-2a-progresion-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Without repeating exercises the progression would never act; 70% bias keeps continuity while 30% randomness preserves novelty. Re-roll stays 100% random because asking for a change expresses wanting variety."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_tolerant_history_parse", "label": "Tolerant History Parse (invalid history ignored, never 400)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-02-fase-2a-progresion-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "history is validated with a separate safeParse; if invalid the backend logs a warning and falls back \u2014 stale data on a user's phone must never break routine generation."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_goal_rep_ranges", "label": "GOAL_REP_RANGE (Perder Peso 12\u201315, Volumen 8\u201312, Mantenerse Activo 10\u201312)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-02-fase-2a-progresion-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "suggestedReps moves from a fixed value to a range: start at the minimum and progress toward the top before adding weight."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_progression_badge", "label": "Progression Direction Badge (\u2191 up / = keep / \u2193 down)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-02-fase-2a-progresion-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}], "edges": [{"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_fase_2a_design", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_progressionservice", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-02-fase-2a-progresion-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_fase_2a_design", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_history_localstorage", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-02-fase-2a-progresion-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_fase_2a_design", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_02_fase_2a_progresion_design_history_summary_transport", "relation": "conceptually_re